'''2017年环西自行车赛'''是第72届[[环西自行车赛|环西自行车赛]]，于2017年8月19日至9月10日进行，此次比赛是2017年UCI世界巡回赛的其中一站比赛<ref name="Cweek">{{cite news |url=http://www.cyclingweekly.co.uk/news/racing/vuelta-espana-set-french-start-2017-281579 |title=Vuelta a España set for French start in 2017 |publisher=Cycling Weekly |date=2016-09-02 |accessdate=2016-09-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160907002142/http://www.cyclingweekly.co.uk/news/racing/vuelta-espana-set-french-start-2017-281579 |archivedate=2016-09-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。比赛共分为21个赛段，起点位于[[法国|法国]][[尼姆|尼姆]]，终点位于[[西班牙|西班牙]][[马德里|马德里]]<ref name="Cnews">{{cite news |url=http://www.cyclingnews.com/news/2017-vuelta-a-espana-to-start-in-nimes/ |title=2017 Vuelta a Espana to start in Nimes |publisher=Cycling News |date=2016-09-02 |accessdate=2016-09-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160905114603/http://www.cyclingnews.com/news/2017-vuelta-a-espana-to-start-in-nimes/ |archivedate=2016-09-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，这是环西自行车赛历史上第三次在西班牙境外开赛<ref name="Cweek"/>。

共有22支车队参加此次比赛，其中18支车队为世界职业车队，另外4支车队则为洲际职业车队<ref>{{cite news|last=Wynn|first=Nigel|title=Wildcard teams revealed for 2017 Vuelta a España|url=http://www.cyclingweekly.com/news/racing/vuelta-a-espana/wildcard-teams-revealed-2017-vuelta-espana-321929|access-date=2017-08-29|work=Cycling Weekly|date=2017-03-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180616075214/http://www.cyclingweekly.com/news/racing/vuelta-a-espana/wildcard-teams-revealed-2017-vuelta-espana-321929|archivedate=2018-06-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最终来自天空车队的英国选手[[克里斯·弗鲁姆|克里斯·弗鲁姆]]夺得此次比赛总冠军<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/cycling/40933339|title=Chris Froome wins Vuelta a Espana win: Stage-by-stage guide to the victory|date=2017-09-10|work=BBC Sport|accessdate=2017-09-19|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180110214407/http://www.bbc.com/sport/cycling/40933339|archivedate=2018-01-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>，与此同时，他还获得象征积分王的绿衫和象征全能王的白衫<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2017/sep/10/chris-froome-wins-vuelta-a-espana-2017|title=Chris Froome seals Vuelta a España title to win historic Vuelta-Tour double|publisher=[[卫报|The Guardian]]|date=2017-09-10|accessdate=2020-09-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618235115/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2017/sep/10/chris-froome-wins-vuelta-a-espana-2017|archivedate=2018-06-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。来自巴林–美利达车队的[[溫琴佐·尼巴利|溫琴佐·尼巴利]]和来自Katusha–Alpecin车队的[[Ilnur_Zakarin|Ilnur Zakarin]]分别获得二三名。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cyclingnews.com/races/vuelta-a-espana-2017/stage-21/results/|title=Chris Froome completes Tour de France - Vuelta a Espana double|publisher=Cycling News|date=2017-09-10|accessdate=2020-09-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603200842/http://www.cyclingnews.com/races/vuelta-a-espana-2017/stage-21/results|archivedate=2019-06-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>

